items.name: Ebyte-amsi-patchless-vehhwbp
items.description: Patchless AMSI bypass using hardware breakpoints and a vectored exception handler to intercept AmsiScanBuffer and AmsiScanString before they execute. The bypass reads the 5th parameter (the AMSI result pointer) from the untouched stack frame, forces a clean result, and returns to the caller without modifying AMSI code in memory.
